title: Star Trek Voyager Elite Force{Phosfate}.zip
description:
{Phosfate}

Prepare to join the Elite Force. When a marauding species captures the U.S.S. 

Voyager, only a member of the newly formed elite security force - The Hazard Team - 

can save the crew, the ship...and the Galaxy itself. Commanded by Lt. Tuvok, you&#039;ll 

leap into action to defend the Voyager from assault, battle through derelict 

spacecraft, infiltrate a Borg cube and take on the ultimate colonization force - all

 the while facing annihilation at every turn. No one said being a hero was easy.

{Phosfate}

Alot of fun and excitement, come with PATCH, DIRECTIONS FOR DOWNLOAD and SERIAL.

Set phasers to frag, and energize!

Enjoy!
